{"tha-ap278:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap278:0.2":"Suvannabibbohanavagga ","tha-ap278:0.3":"6 Potthakadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap278:1.1":"“Sattharam dhammamarabbha, ","tha-ap278:1.2":"sanghancapi mahesinam; ","tha-ap278:1.3":"Potthadanam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap278:1.4":"dakkhineyye anuttare. ","tha-ap278:2.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap278:2.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap278:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap278:2.4":"potthadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap278:3.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap278:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap278:3.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap278:4.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma potthakadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap278:5.1":"Potthakadayakattherassapadanam chattham. "}